name: Anycubic Kossel Pulley
pre_gcode: M140 S{bed_temp}   ; need to heat the bed
M190 S{bed_temp}   ; wait for bed temperature
M104 S{temp}       ; need to heat the nozzle
M109 S{temp}       ; wait for nozzle temperature
G1 F200 E3              ;extrude 3mm of feed stock
G92 E0                  ;zero the extruded length again
post_gcode: G1 E-1 F300      ;retract the filament a bit before lifting the nozzle, to release some of the pressure
G1 F120 Z+1 E-5        ;move Z up a bit and retract filament even more
